reviewText: McLeod's Daughters is one of the best movie entertainment I have ever watched. I love the setting, in Australia outback, I love the cast, I love what they are doing. There is nothing boring about this series. I wish there were more out there like these. They are especially good for mother and daughter to watch. Love it!

reviewText: I LOVE THIS SERIES. OTHERWISE THEY ARE GREAT.THIS IS THE ONLY REASON I DID NOT GIVE IT A 5 STAR RATING.
